.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH webp-doctor 1  "doctor " 
.SH NAME
doctor \- Diagnose the environment: PATH drop\-in shadows, config, terminal, threads
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdoctor\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Diagnose the environment: PATH drop\-in shadows, config, terminal, threads.
.PP
Exits 0 even with warnings; 1 only on a real error (an invalid config file).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
